    narr:generatedFrom "25fb8818b2c21243b69f5bf640b183eef02428e4" ;
    narr:narration """Governance and trust in agentic systems have evolved from early ethical debates over [extraction and consent](narr:Position_ConsentEthicsAdvisorRecording) toward a technical framework centered on [agentic boundaries](narr:Narrative_AgentBoundsAndEscalation). The current trajectory emphasizes [per-task scoped permissions](narr:Narrative_PerTaskScopedPermissions), utilizing OAuth-style single-use grants to replace broad access. This shift is supported by [hard vs. soft segmentation](narr:Narrative_HardVsSoftSegmentation), which distinguishes between proprietary client isolation and shared organizational perspectives. Trust is maintained through [anti-hallucination via citation](narr:Narrative_AntiHallucinationViaCitation), though this introduces a critical dependency on [non-negotiable provenance](narr:Narrative_HubMemoryProvenanceNonNegotiable) to ensure that summaries remain anchored to primary sources. The system further constrains agent behavior through [appropriateness gates](narr:Principle_AppropriatenessGate) and [disclosure-by-default](narr:Principle_DisclosureDefault), ensuring agents operate within [regulatory boundaries](narr:Position_ProposalRegulatorySafeguard) while leveraging [Vouch identity infrastructure](narr:Narrative_VouchIdentityForAgents). Data sovereignty is treated as a foundational trust differentiator, with [user-owned repositories](narr:Obs_UserOwnedRepo) serving as the primary storage model.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AgentBoundsAndEscalation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_AntiHallucinationViaCitation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_HardVsSoftSegmentation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_HubMemoryProvenanceNonNegotiable> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_PerTaskScopedPermissions> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_VouchIdentityForAgents> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_AntiHallucination> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DiscoveryConsultantAgentBoundaryQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_DiscoveryConsultantOAuthScopeQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletAgentBoundsQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ScarletVouchPermissionsQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_StaleGraphDanger> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_UserOwnedRepo> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_TrustContractPrincipledEscalation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Position_CoLocationMemory> ;
